{
  "_comment": "Curated R2 layer for the Fonderie brain (BRAIN_PLAN.md Phase 1/2). Hand-maintained: closed-domain alias edges + recipes + invariants that structural extraction cannot infer. Merged into brain.json by scripts/generate-brain.mjs. Grows from corpus misses (experiments/brain-2026-07).",
